4-LOM was an ambitious protocol droid who overwrote his own programming in order to embark on a life of crime. Following the Battle of Hoth, 4-LOM was hired by the Sith Lord known as Darth Vader to capture Han Solo, captain of the Millennium Falcon and hero of the Rebel Alliance."